706934f-a.text:
Sumpter Street, south side, east of Patchen Ave., showing the Bretzer house of 1850, still standing in (1929). In our curtilage of this house, is the rear of two frame homes which front on Fulton Street, and bear Nos. 1827-1829.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster. Collection.
